originalText.text: Dr. Barbieri is the Most Amazing Doctor!!! She is so knowledgeable and caring with all her patients. She takes the time to look at you instead of her computer and truly listen to your health concerns. Then she proceeds to come up with the most empowering suggestion for your personal health goals. No other doctor in 50 years has made me feel so supported. I am so incredibly grateful I have found her for my care and anyone else who I know needs her care and expertise!! Thank you!!!

originalText.text: Dr. Barbieri is the lens that all doctors should have on women’s health.  Within 15 minutes of our first conversation I wished she was my primary doctor for the last 30 years. She put pieces of my health care history together that no one had connected or tried to connect. She took the time for a comprehensive lens. For the first time I feel complete trust that my doctor sees my unique individual profile and is fully present to support me live a long healthy life.

originalText.text: Dr. Barbieri treats each patient as an individual. While she is a wonderful gynecologist, her concern for her patients goes beyond gynecological matters to include the whole person. I highly recommend her.

originalText.text: This is THE practice for women who are in need of truly attentive, supportive, and proactive care at a pivotal point - the season of midlife change. It was an unfortunate event that led me to Dr. Barbieri, but I am truly grateful to have discovered her. I recommend her without hesitation.

originalText.text: I had a wonderful experience.  The staff is genuinely caring, friendly and accomodating.   The office is beautiful, clean and inviting.  I've been a patient of Dr. Barbieri for many years.  She is an amazing doctor.  She's thorough, kind and patient and I love her holistic approach.  She is not hurried and gives you time to ask questions.   I highly recommend Dr. Barbieri and her practice.
